org.swerverobotics.library.interfaces

Class Acceleration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.swerverobotics.library.interfaces.Acceleration

  • public class Acceleration
extends java.lang.Object
    Acceleration represents a directed acceleration in three-space. Units are as specified in sensor initialization. The time at which the data was acquired is provided so as to facilitate integration of accelerations.
